'''2019年美洲杯决赛'''（{{lang-en|2019 Copa América Final}}）是2019年7月7日在[[巴西|巴西]][[里约热内卢|里约热内卢]][[马拉卡纳体育场|马拉卡纳体育场]]进行的一场足球比赛，旨在确定[[2019年美洲杯|2019年美洲杯]]冠军。

比赛由东道主[[巴西國家足球隊|巴西]]对阵[[秘魯國家足球隊|秘鲁]]，最终巴西3:1赢得了队伍历史上第9座[[美洲杯|美洲杯]]冠军，而这也是自[[2007年美洲国家杯|2007年]]以来巴西的首个冠军<ref name="2007-1">{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2019/jul/07/copa-america-brazil-peru-final-gabriel-jesus|title=Brazil end Copa América drought with victory over Peru in final|date=2019-07-07|website=theguardian.com|publisher=Guardian News & Media Limited|access-date=2019-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721175213/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2019/jul/07/copa-america-brazil-peru-final-gabriel-jesus|archive-date=2019-07-21|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="2007-2">{{Cite web|url=https://www.goal.com/es-cl/news/4778/main/2016/06/23/23609392/historia-de-la-copa-am%C3%A9rica-2007-robinho-fue-messi|title=En 2007, Brasil le ganó a Argentina la Copa América. {{!}} Goal.com|website=www.goal.com|year=2007|language=es|access-date=2020-07-21|archive-date=2021-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210719064454/https://www.goal.com/es-cl/news/4778/main/2016/06/23/23609392/historia-de-la-copa-am%C3%A9rica-2007-robinho-fue-messi}}</ref><ref name="2007-3">{{Cite web|url=https://www.alairelibre.cl/noticias/deportes/copa-america/venezuela-2007/brasil-destrozo-el-favoritismo-argentino-y-se-corono-bicampeon-de/2007-07-15/190805.html|title=Brasil destrozó el favoritismo argentino y se coronó bicampeón de América|last=Comunicaciones|first=Compañia Chilena de|website=alairelibre.cl|language=es|date=2007-07-15|access-date=2007-07-15|archive-date=2022-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220407094403/https://www.alairelibre.cl/noticias/deportes/copa-america/venezuela-2007/brasil-destrozo-el-favoritismo-argentino-y-se-corono-bicampeon-de/2007-07-15/190805.html}}</ref>。

==背景==
2019年美洲杯决赛是巴西主办的第五届美洲杯比赛。这是秘鲁第三次进入决赛，其中前两次都获得了冠军。他们上一次夺冠（国际赛事）是在[[1975年美洲國家盃|1975年]]<ref name="calendar">{{cite web |url=http://www.conmebol.com/es/conmebol-y-comite-organizador-local-definen-calendario-de-la-conmebol-copa-america-brasil-2019 |title=CONMEBOL y Comité Organizador Local definen calendario de la CONMEBOL Copa América Brasil 2019 |trans-title=CONMEBOL and Local Organizing Committee define the calendar of the CONMEBOL Copa América Brazil 2019 |publisher=CONMEBOL.com |date=2018-12-18 |access-date=2018-12-18 |language=es |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190601135504/http://www.conmebol.com/es/conmebol-y-comite-organizador-local-definen-calendario-de-la-conmebol-copa-america-brasil-2019 |archive-date=2019-06-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2019/jul/02/argentina-brazil-copa-america-match-report|title=Firmino and Jesus strike as Brazil sink Argentina in Copa América semi-final|date=2019-07-02|work=Guardian|accessdate=2019-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721175222/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2019/jul/02/argentina-brazil-copa-america-match-report|archive-date=2019-07-21|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2019/jul/04/peru-set-up-brazil-clash-in-copa-america-final-after-resounding-win-over-chile|title=Peru set up Brazil clash in Copa América final after resounding win over Chile|date=2019-07-04|work=Guardian|accessdate=2019-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721175323/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2019/jul/04/peru-set-up-brazil-clash-in-copa-america-final-after-resounding-win-over-chile|archive-date=2019-07-21|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://peru.com/retro/peru/peru-campeon-copa-america-1975-fotos-noticia-436255|title=Perú, campeón de la Copa América 1975|last=Peru.com|date=2016-02-03|website=Perú.com|language=es|access-date=2016-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203091136/http://peru.com/retro/peru/peru-campeon-copa-america-1975-fotos-noticia-436255|archive-date=2016-02-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://elcomercio.pe/deporte-total/seleccion/copa-america-1975-gol-sotil-le-dio-titulo-peru-236281|title=Copa América 1975: el gol de Sotil que le dio título a Perú|last=Elcomercio.pe|first=Redacción|date=2015-10-10|website=El Comercio|language=es|access-date=2015-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190704044600/https://elcomercio.pe/deporte-total/seleccion/copa-america-1975-gol-sotil-le-dio-titulo-peru-236281|archive-date=2019-07-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同时，这是巴西第19次进入决赛，其中8次夺冠。巴西队上一次赢得美洲杯冠军是在委内瑞拉举行的2007年美洲杯，当时巴西3:0击败阿根廷了成功夺冠<ref name="2007-1" /><ref name="2007-2" /><ref name="2007-3" />。

